First-run setup wizard for demo, Gmail, or IMAP/SMTP

Usage: mxr setup [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --demo       Legacy helper that drops a fake-provider account into the current config. Prefer `mxr demo` for an isolated 50k-message demo profile
      --key <KEY>  Account key to use when writing the demo entry. Defaults to `demo`. Used to namespace the entry — handy if you want to keep a real account configured alongside [default: demo]
      --force      Skip the safety check that refuses to overwrite an existing account with the same key
  -h, --help       Print help
